data.eml:eml: Mycale (Oxymycale) klausjanusorum sp. nov. (Porifera: Demospongiae: Poecilosclerida) from Flores Sea deep water, Indonesia

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Van Soest, Rob W. M. (2018): Mycale (Oxymycale) klausjanusorum sp. nov. (Porifera: Demospongiae: Poecilosclerida) from Flores Sea deep water, Indonesia. Zootaxa 4466 (1): 49-60, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4466.1.6
